  <TextWithYoutube
    title='Mending Wall'
    video='https://www.youtube.com/embed/nZmymwFIJhA?si=7JYrMorzpJXmCEL3'
  >
    <p>
      This song was included on <b>Song of the Poet</b> as part of the song cycle
      of poems that I put in musical settings. By giving the classic poem of Robert
      Frost a Latin twist, the meaning is extended as a commentary on the hatred
      so often directed at our southern neighbors who contribute so much to our economy
      and culture. Special thanks to Crystal Soto for putting the video together
      and to Roberto Perez for providing his running commentary in Spanish as sonoro
      deploring bigotry.
    </p>
